Package: geometr
Title: Generate and process geometric shapes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Steffen", "Ehrmann", email = "steffen@funroll-loops.de",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2958-0796"))
Description: The geometr package provides a simplified approach to generating
    and manipulating geometries at vertex level. Vertices are stored in tables 
    (not lists) and can simply be transformed into a wide array of spatial objects.
URL: https://github.com/EhrmannS/geometr
BugReports: https://github.com/EhrmannS/geometr/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-3
